commit fc8bcee8cd25beb019ac76fc4e33181a0e426ec9
Author: Alexia Ingerson <alexia.ingerson@intel.com>
Date:   Tue May 7 15:44:52 2024 -0700

    ofi: quick implementation of FI_THREAD_DOMAIN
    
    move fid_domain and fid_av into atl_ofi_prov_ep_t and initialize separate
    domains and AVs for each endpoint. This reduces bottlenecks for domain
    resources such as progress engines
    
    Signed-off-by: Alexia Ingerson <alexia.ingerson@intel.com>

